## Section 10 — Recovery Decision Governance

Authority is mechanical. Judgment is human. This section governs decision logic after Tier-0 is VERIFIED. Filesystem truth is re-established first, derived systems follow, runtime behavior is last. Human judgment is constrained by authority. Automation exists to stop; humans decide what happens next. All rules unchanged.

