## Section 16 — Recovery Invariants & Data Reconciliation Law

Authoritative truth: TrueNAS ZFS datasets. Reconstructable: PostgreSQL, Redis, containers, VM OSes, Proxmox host OS. Backup copies: Synology NAS, Filen Cloud.

Recovery order:

1. Platform safety
2. Authoritative filesystem state
3. Rebuild reconstructable state
4. Reconcile applications to filesystem truth
5. Re-establish monitoring and backup trust

Reconciliation is mandatory even if no error is visible. All rules unchanged.

